com.aionemu.gameserver.model.gameobjects
Class VisibleObject

java.lang.Object
  com.aionemu.gameserver.model.gameobjects.AionObject
      com.aionemu.gameserver.model.gameobjects.VisibleObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Creature, Gatherable, StaticObject
public abstract class VisibleObject
extends AionObject

This class is representing visible objects. It's a base class for all in-game objects that can be spawned in the world at some particular position (such as players, npcs).

Objects of this class, as can be spawned in game, can be seen by other visible objects. To keep track of which objects are already "known" by this visible object and which are not, VisibleObject is containing KnownList which is responsible for holding this information.

Author:
-Nemesiss-
